labels.privacy label detail: Non-differentially private synthetic data.  Produced using a fully conditional multilple imputation algorithm comprised of a sequence of decision trees trained on the target data.  Each  feature value in a given record is synthesized one at a time: the values of the preceding synthesized features are fed into the decision tree trained to predict the current feature.
